<!-- Agent guidance: .dev/HUDs & Overlays/Player HUD Overview.md; lib/json/PCS.json (PC fields). -->
<!-- XML Exact height is 200; 8.5x11 aspect ratio means the width is 154.5

Standard dot images are 6.3x6.3 pixels.
Standard dot-lines are five standard dots wide with 3.4 pixel spacing between them.
Large dot images are 11.3x11.3 pixels.
Large dot-lines are five large dots wide with 6.8 pixel spacing between them.
Standard box images are 8.0x8.0 pixels.
Standard box-lines are ten standard boxes wide with 4.2 pixel spacing between them.

*** PAGE 1 STANDARD DOT LINES *** == ATTRIBUTES ==
9 standard dot-lines in a 3x3 grid.
Grid top-left is at 28.5 -66.8
Row spacing is -7.7 pixels.
Column spacing is 49.7 pixels
Dot images: dot_yellow, dot_white
Dot ids: <dot_image_name>_<attribute_key>_<slot_number>
  E.g. dot_yellow_strength_1, dot_white_dexterity_2, etc.

  == SKILLS ==
27 standard dot-lines in a 3x9 grid.
Grid top-left is at 28.5 -94.0
Row spacing is -7.9 pixels.
Column spacing is 49.7 pixels
Dot images: dot_yellow, dot_white
Dot ids: <dot_image_name>_<skill_key>_<slot_number>
  E.g. dot_yellow_athletics_1, dot_white_animalKen_2, etc.

  == BOX TRACKERS ==
3 standard box-lines in a 2x2 grid, with the bottom-right grid being empty.
Grid top-left is at 108.5 -173.05
Row spacing is -12.1 pixels.
Column spacing is 88.4 pixels.
Box images (first and third grid cells): box_yellow, box_grey, box_red
Box images (second grid cell): box_white, box_black, box_red
Box ids: <box_image_name>_<tracker_key>_<slot_number>
  E.g. box_yellow_health_1, box_grey_willpower_2, etc.

  == BLOOD POTENCY ==
1 large dot-line.
Dot-line top-left is at 103.3 -184.2
Dot images: dot_large_red, dot_large_white
Dot ids: <dot_image_name>_bloodPotency_<slot_number>
  E.g. dot_large_red_bloodPotency_1, dot_large_white_bloodPotency_2, etc.

 -->

